comments: The ball is kicked by Doncic (DAL).
Harden (HOU) reaches in and makes contact to Doncic's (DAL) arm during his driving shot attempt.

Doncic (DAL) establishes himself in a legal guarding position in Covington's (HOU) path.  When Doncic contests Covington's driving shot attempt, he is retreating his arms into a vertical position when the marginal contact occurs with Covington's right arm.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) moves backwards into Westbrook's (HOU) lower body while he's airborne and the contact affects his ability to get to the loose ball.
Porzingis (DAL) holds Harden's (HOU) arm during the loose ball and the contact affects his ability to move freely.
Curry (DAL) makes marginal contact to Harden's (HOU) left arm during his drive.
House Jr. (HOU) does not step out of bounds.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes contact to Covington's (HOU) body and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) briefly engages with Finney-Smith (DAL), whose backwards momentum carries him away from the contact during the inbound.
Westbrook (HOU) commits a take foul on Curry (DAL).
Porzingis (DAL) briefly grasps Tucker's (HOU) arm during the rebound but the contact is marginal.
Finney-Smith (DAL) swipes down and makes contact to Harden's (HOU) arm prior to the start of his upward shooting motion.
Westbrook (HOU) and Burke (DAL) make incidental contact with each other during the loose ball.
Kleber (DAL) makes incidental contact with House Jr. (HOU) as both players jump towards each other for the rebound.
Westbrook (HOU) steps out of bounds during his dribble.
House Jr. (HOU) makes marginal contact with Burke (DAL) that does not cause him to lose his balance during the drive to the basket.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Doncic (DAL) makes clean contact with the ball and avoids making contact with Tucker (HOU) that dislodges him during the loose ball.

Replay review of the offensive foul called on Doncic (DAL) pursuant to a coach's challenge is deemed unsuccessful. 
 Tucker (HOU) established himself in a legal guarding position outside of the RA prior to when contact occurred during Doncic's driving shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in House Jr.'s (HOU) path and he is firming up when the contact occurs.
